graph TD
    accTitle: Alignment Workflow
    accDescr: Processing merged FASTQ files through BWA-MEM alignment, sorting, duplicate marking, and final indexing.

    merged_fastqs[📦 **prealignment** FASTQs] --> bwa_mem[⚙️ **bwa_mem** per flowcell/lane]
    bwa_mem --> bwa_mem_merge[⚙️ **merge** lanes]
    bwa_mem_merge --> samtools_sort_1[⚙️ **samtools** sort]
    samtools_sort_1 --> samtools_index_1[⚙️ **samtools** index]
    samtools_sort_1 --> samtools_extract[⚙️ **extract** split by chr]
    samtools_extract --> picard_mark[⚙️ **picard** MarkDuplicates]
    picard_mark --> samtools_merge_chr[⚙️ **merge** chromosomes]
    samtools_merge_chr --> samtools_sort_2[⚙️ **samtools** sort]
    samtools_sort_2 --> samtools_index_2[⚙️ **samtools** index]
    samtools_sort_2 --> final_bam[📦 **alignment** BAM]
    
    final_bam -.-> snv_module{{🔗 **SNV_indels** module}}
    final_bam -.-> cnv_module{{🔗 **CNV_SV** module}}
    final_bam -.-> qc_module{{🔗 **QC** module}}

    classDef primary fill:#dbeafe,stroke:#2563eb,stroke-width:2px,color:#1e3a5f
    classDef success fill:#dcfce7,stroke:#16a34a,stroke-width:2px,color:#14532d
    classDef accent fill:#ede9fe,stroke:#7c3aed,stroke-width:2px,color:#3b0764

    class merged_fastqs primary
    class final_bam success
    class snv_module,cnv_module,qc_module accent
